headline: Sempra Infrastructure to supply LNG from Port Arthur Phase 2 project in US
summary: The 20-year agreement with EQT will see LNG procured on a free-on-board basis with pricing indexed to the Henry Hub.

headline: Sempra and EQT Sign 20-Year LNG Supply Deal for Port Arthur Phase 2
summary: Sempra Infrastructure and EQT Corporation have signed a 20-year sales and purchase agreement for 2 million tonnes per annum of LNG from the Port Arthur LNG Phase 2 project in Texas.
